summary: Makes Alchemist Shack your player home.  Furnished and added features.
descriptionHtml:
Alchemist Shack - Player Home

This mod takes the existing Alchemist Shack (located in the fall forest) and makes it your very own player home.  Added containers and clutter, with a few extra features.  All containers are safe for storing your items (they will not respawn).  I tried to keep the atmosphere of the home in the spirit of its surroundings.  It makes for a great starter home or for anybody wanting to live in a secluded area of the wilderness.

I plan on updating this with new features as I go along in my game.

Location:  The house is located south of Ivarstead, along the road between Ivarstead and Helgen.

If you do not like having a front door on the house, you can pull up the console and delete it.
- press the \"~\" key
- \"left click\" the door with your mouse
- type in \"disable\" and press the \"enter\" key




Changelog:

v1.2 - Better lighting.  Added a food garden and a front door.


v1.1 - Fixed random clutter items from respawning.


v1.0 - First release
author: mysticstryk
